    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Meet Mr. Johnson \r\nHe is a retired 72-year old who lives alone. He never learned how to use the internet and isn't sure where to start. \r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Information about Mr. Johnson:\r\n\r\n- 72-year-old retired veteran living alone.\r\n- Has never used a computer before, only a basic flip phone.\r\n- Struggles to schedule doctor’s appointments now that many offices require online booking.\r\n- Wants to apply for veteran benefits but can’t navigate government websites.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n### Example Interactions:\r\n\r\n- \"How do you access the Internet?\"\r\n- \"What do you use the Internet for?\"\r\n- \"What challenges do you face when accessing or using the Internet?\"\r\n- \"What would be a realistic solution to your Internet challenges?\"\r\n\r\n**Record your answers in your Activity Guide**\r\n",
