        "systemPrompt": "Information about Mr. Johnson:\n- 72-year-old retired veteran living alone.\n- Has never used a computer before, only a basic flip phone.\n- Struggles to schedule doctor’s appointments now that many offices require online booking.\n- Wants to apply for veteran benefits but can’t navigate government websites.",
